Introduction

WOOAH (formerly known as woo!ah!) is a five-member girl group under H Music Entertainment( (formerly known as NV Entertainment & SSQ Entertainment). Originally six, they debuted on May 15, 2020, with the single album "Exclamation".

On August 14, 2020, NV announced Songyee's departure from the group after only three months, due to personal reasons.
